OL,3,CMan who committed hate crimes jailed
OL,4,Cfor antisemitic abuse of police
OL,6,FA man who committed multiple hate
OL,7,Fcrimes and assaults, including against
OL,8,Fpolice officers, has been jailed for
OL,9,F18 months.
OL,11,FIn June 2025, Rasheed Jama, 20,
OL,12,FCardiff, committed a racially
OL,13,Faggravated assault on a police officer
OL,14,Fand subjected them to antisemitic
OL,15,Fabuse.
OL,17,FJama then went on to use antisemitic
OL,18,Flanguage against a police officer
OL,19,Fagain, in a separate incident in
OL,20,FAugust.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
