OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779991869
OL,3,CMan who committed hate crimes jailed
OL,4,Cfor antisemitic abuse of police
OL,6,FIn a third incident, he committed an
OL,7,Funprovoked attack on a man in a pub in
OL,8,FPenarth, Vale of Glamorgan, where he
OL,9,Fhit the man on the head with a hammer.
OL,11,FJama pleaded guilty to nine offences -
OL,12,Freligiously aggravated assault, four
OL,13,Fcounts of assaulting an emergency
OL,14,Fworker, wounding, possession of an
OL,15,Foffensive weapon, racially aggravated
OL,16,Fassault by beating and religiously
OL,17,Faggravated harassment.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
