CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1779991869
OL,3,CMan who committed hate crimes jailed
OL,4,Cfor antisemitic abuse of police
OL,6,FJama was sentenced at Cardiff Crown
OL,7,FCourt on 27 May 2026 where Judge
OL,8,FFelstead described the crimes as
OL,9,F"disgusting and utterly reprehensible".
OL,11,FPaul Jenkins of the CPS said: "Hate
OL,12,Fcrimes, of any form, are abhorrent and
OL,13,Fhave no place in our society.
OL,15,F"The CPS will not hesitate to
OL,16,Fprosecute these offences whenever the
OL,17,Flegal test is met.
